{"id": "ChIJA5uBzst_hYARVF2wGt7w4Xc", "rating": 4.5, "userRatingCount": 149, "displayName": {"text": "Binge Coffee House", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJA5uBzst_hYARVF2wGt7w4Xc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GSFVYaElWREphZDFwME5VZG5XblJ1U0VaYVQwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Just checked out Binge Coffee House and I’m impressed ☕✨\n\nThis Vietnamese-inspired spot is a whole vibe, super cozy, study-friendly, and definitely a go-to if you’re in the Berkeley area. They’ve got everything from authentic Vietnamese iced coffee to unique matcha creations and tasty bites like bánh mì and pandan waffles.\n\nI tried the banana matcha and wow… sweet, creamy, and perfectly balanced with salted cashews on top 🤤🔥 that sweet + salty combo really hit.\n\nThey’ve got a wide variety of matcha flavors too (banana, pistachio, and more), so there’s plenty to explore.\n\nHighly recommend if you’re looking for a chill spot with good energy and even better drinks 💚", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Just checked out Binge Coffee House and I’m impressed ☕✨\n\nThis Vietnamese-inspired spot is a whole vibe, super cozy, study-friendly, and definitely a go-to if you’re in the Berkeley area. They’ve got everything from authentic Vietnamese iced coffee to unique matcha creations and tasty bites like bánh mì and pandan waffles.\n\nI tried the banana matcha and wow… sweet, creamy, and perfectly balanced with salted cashews on top 🤤🔥 that sweet + salty combo really hit.\n\nThey’ve got a wide variety of matcha flavors too (banana, pistachio, and more), so there’s plenty to explore.\n\nHighly recommend if you’re looking for a chill spot with good energy and even better drinks 💚", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Tony Bowles", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103546538818781913871/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVMJ5-zKKscvcVRXSQmg3UsLIvtm46G8PF5szdqI-_bKj7CpDg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-08T20:32:54.589102541Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GSFVYaElWREphZDFwME5VZG5XblJ1U0VaYVQwRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GSFVYaElWREphZDFwME5VZG5XblJ1U0VaYVQwRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857fcbce819b03:0x77e1f0de1ab05d54"}, {"name": "places/ChIJA5uBzst_hYARVF2wGt7w4Xc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Jek9XaHJURXhNY1hOWFpGcFRVa1ZDV0V0VUxYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "My wife and I wanted to check out this spot on our way to Vallejo.\n\nService was quick and efficient. The worker was able to explain the drinks that we asked about.\n\nAmbiance is a cool little spot. Had some searing but it's not a big cafe.\n\nWe orders the Ube Viet Coffee and Viet Coffee w/cheese foam\n\nWe asked for “less sweet” and it was perfect.\n\nI really liked the taste of their Vietnamese Coffee and the foams did not overpower the coffee\n\nDefinitely would come back to try other drinks.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "My wife and I wanted to check out this spot on our way to Vallejo.\n\nService was quick and efficient. The worker was able to explain the drinks that we asked about.\n\nAmbiance is a cool little spot. Had some searing but it's not a big cafe.\n\nWe orders the Ube Viet Coffee and Viet Coffee w/cheese foam\n\nWe asked for “less sweet” and it was perfect.\n\nI really liked the taste of their Vietnamese Coffee and the foams did not overpower the coffee\n\nDefinitely would come back to try other drinks.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Rolly Junio", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113718837779482930400/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIbof2geXxYWJYBe8-RVDoL-dIwyFVdIHO8OxRjxLY2B_kCjA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-17T06:57:30.964214257Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Jek9XaHJURXhNY1hOWFpGcFRVa1ZDV0V0VUxYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Jek9XaHJURXhNY1hOWFpGcFRVa1ZDV0V0VUxYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857fcbce819b03:0x77e1f0de1ab05d54"}, {"name": "places/ChIJA5uBzst_hYARVF2wGt7w4Xc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pFMVQya3dRMU5uWm10eVIxUnBWRlIwVEVwMlVFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "9 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "got the blueberry matcha and absolutely LOVED IT! inside the store is cozy and nice place to study as well. friendly staff and great customer service. the blueberry matcha was more on the sweeter side and I would add extra shot of matcha. will be coming back to try their other matcha flavors!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "got the blueberry matcha and absolutely LOVED IT! inside the store is cozy and nice place to study as well. friendly staff and great customer service. the blueberry matcha was more on the sweeter side and I would add extra shot of matcha. will be coming back to try their other matcha flavors!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "oakinawa", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106984470328450027157/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7IqUCvJfMgCFKk7U9h08qlXuA11b0LRWdESH3NP4vEYy74J-xwQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2025-10-10T07:04:58.690464641Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pFMVQya3dRMU5uWm10eVIxUnBWRlIwVEVwMlVFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pFMVQya3dRMU5uWm10eVIxUnBWRlIwVEVwMlVFRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857fcbce819b03:0x77e1f0de1ab05d54"}, {"name": "places/ChIJA5uBzst_hYARVF2wGt7w4Xc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psZk5EZGhhMWRwU201Sk1UWnVPVXRIWVdkSVNFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I love their egg coffee. It doesn’t taste like egg at all — instead, it makes the coffee flavor richer and more intense. Sometimes I even wonder if they actually add egg, because you can’t taste it directly. But the drink is amazing, both in flavor and in the coffee itself.Be prepared  ahead they always packed with plenty of orders .", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I love their egg coffee. It doesn’t taste like egg at all — instead, it makes the coffee flavor richer and more intense. Sometimes I even wonder if they actually add egg, because you can’t taste it directly. But the drink is amazing, both in flavor and in the coffee itself.Be prepared  ahead they always packed with plenty of orders .", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Mittar Pwar", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103473733424693215916/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUruDwyx10mQcX0vMd85raenFiRvWQYMKOBX1QT9qW6FaSHuE4Wxw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-18T15:15:30.076025751Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psZk5EZGhhMWRwU201Sk1UWnVPVXRIWVdkSVNFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psZk5EZGhhMWRwU201Sk1UWnVPVXRIWVdkSVNFRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857fcbce819b03:0x77e1f0de1ab05d54"}, {"name": "places/ChIJA5uBzst_hYARVF2wGt7w4Xc/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VLbTcyWlBqNThlX3dnRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Binge Coffee is serving up some creative drinks — I tried the ube matcha and strawberry matcha, and both were on point.\n\nThe ube matcha was rich, earthy, and perfectly balanced — not too sweet ( ordered half sweet) and the ube added a creamy, nutty layer that paired well with the matcha’s bitterness.\nThe strawberry matcha was lighter, refreshing, and a little fruity without tasting artificial. Visually stunning too — they nail the aesthetic game here.\n\nStaff was quick, friendly, and the vibe is modern but relaxed. You can tell they care about quality and flavor.\n\nThe store is on the small side so it gets crowded. Their AC could use some work too.\n\nBottom line: If you’re into matcha and want something beyond the usual, Binge is a must. Fun flavors, done right.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Binge Coffee is serving up some creative drinks — I tried the ube matcha and strawberry matcha, and both were on point.\n\nThe ube matcha was rich, earthy, and perfectly balanced — not too sweet ( ordered half sweet) and the ube added a creamy, nutty layer that paired well with the matcha’s bitterness.\nThe strawberry matcha was lighter, refreshing, and a little fruity without tasting artificial. Visually stunning too — they nail the aesthetic game here.\n\nStaff was quick, friendly, and the vibe is modern but relaxed. You can tell they care about quality and flavor.\n\nThe store is on the small side so it gets crowded. Their AC could use some work too.\n\nBottom line: If you’re into matcha and want something beyond the usual, Binge is a must. Fun flavors, done right.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "C W", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115816144824453545330/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKCM11KcR9gJziJQCX7cEpnjr9qzwhci67xNqq228VvyvKxIw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2025-06-28T23:43:13.031584184Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VLbTcyWlBqNThlX3dnRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VLbTcyWlBqNThlX3dnRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857fcbce819b03:0x77e1f0de1ab05d54"}], 